{"tid":2284973,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"為確保暖 “雞” 功能正常 肯德基次世代主機「KFConsole」宣布延期至 12 月上市","createTime":"2020-11-13T17:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T16:15:02.000Z","uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"026e77d33c299d32c36b3e2b41253885d57309ff","tid":2284973,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T17:34:43.000Z","msg":"連鎖速食業者肯德基（KFC）旗下遊戲部門 KFC Gaming 官方 Twitter 於美國時間 11 月 12 日宣布，原定 11 月 12 日上市的新主機「KFConsole」，為了確保其暖 &ldquo;雞&rdquo; 功能正常發揮，將延期至 12 月 11 日上市。<br />\nKFConsole」是肯德基於 6 月 11 日發表的全新遊戲主機，採用受「肯德基烤雞桶」啟發的圓筒狀造型設計，內建創新的「烤雞室」，具備能烤出香噴噴烤雞的獨創功能。配備頻率高達 11GHz 的 Zinger 處理器。支援真 4K 解析度與 120FPS 更新率。同時提供跨平台相容性。最適合想要征服飢餓與虛擬戰場的玩家。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=52&amp;v=73SqN-ueP7g&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D52%26v%3D73SqN-ueP7g%26feature%3Demb_title&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOImLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=9db9d797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=52&amp;v=73SqN-ueP7g&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=206402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D206402&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOImLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=775932a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=206402</a>"},{"pid":"b55b3b41ac78bcf165f4dc4f0b09b303a5338c04","tid":2284973,"uid":80719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T17:48:31.000Z","msg":"靠粒u熱力烤雞？"},{"pid":"caadb8b010839ecc5165602542dab7cfe7001ce3","tid":2284973,"uid":61954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T18:02:45.000Z","msg":"提早4月1?"},{"pid":"c155c892ac041509a50bf9bc3c08f1fcb54572e5","tid":2284973,"uid":346404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T18:26:27.000Z","msg":"有種難以形容既膠